{"tid":1178423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國商會稱向特區政府就逃犯修例提8問題　要求回應","createTime":"2019-05-30T11:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T12:37:09.000Z","uid":41404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"557fcdf84dcabe789407d2fa474a840db9c9f22e","tid":1178423,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"美國商會發表聲明，認為香港未為修訂《逃犯條例》做好準備，修例有太多不確定性，必須向社會進一步說明，又說既然有關「漏洞」已存在20年，看不到現階段為何要急於通過修例解決。商會昨日就修訂《逃犯條例》與政務司司長張建宗會面，向特區政府提出8條問題，要求對方回應。<br />\n<br />\n商會說，據報有30個外交人員反對修例，並表示其所屬國家可能因此檢視與香港的關係，特區政府如何回應。商會又指，3名本港法官表達對修例深感不安，又認為修例不可行，特區政府如何確保本港法治不因強行通過修例而受損。<br />\n<br />\n商會亦要求特區政府澄清，技術上如何確保修例後，本港的新聞及言論自由不會受到損；以及香港本身已屬低犯罪率的城市，為何要在承受法治聲譽受損的風險下，追求進一步打擊犯罪行為。商會希望當局說明，修例後如何確保提出引渡的司法管轄區有公平審訊。"},{"pid":"ef01b8c06d29afcd5d78cf0b68ffdeb21aa63dcc","tid":1178423,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:41:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.amcham.org.hk/news/press-release-proposed-fugitive-offenders-ordinance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amcham.org.hk%2Fnews%2Fpress-release-proposed-fugitive-offenders-ordinance&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1TKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=c365c2b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amcham.org.hk/news/press-release-proposed-fugitive-offenders-ordinance</a>"},{"pid":"3ac3c3112aeb1e91b6b1573764db2476880227e4","tid":1178423,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"立法會法律顧問幾條問題回答咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3958e1f13e61bd7548f988806080c8acfd2b3189","tid":1178423,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭回應稱，很快便上任特首兩年，她在特首就職禮上曾承諾，秉持要成功落實「一國兩制」，維護法治及香港的傳統價值，並確認法治是香港最重要的核心價值，而修例處理台灣殺人案，正是彰顯法治、令香港核心價值得以確立的證明。"},{"pid":"628f63bafb4f79bd36570fd5ebdb0dc592ee9a41","tid":1178423,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ac3c3112aeb1e91b6b1573764db2476880227e4","tid":1178423,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"立法會法律顧問幾條問題回答咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/逃犯條例/article/20190516/special/1557944282554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%2Farticle%2F20190516%2Fspecial%2F1557944282554&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1TKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=6f91789d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%2Farticle%2F20190516%2Fspecial%2F1557944282554&h=89aa3f75\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/逃犯條例/article/20190516/special/1557944282554</a><br />\n睇報導唔知有冇答晒。"},{"pid":"0c2f972f63de7bc13e2413116764640fece37993","tid":1178423,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>商會說，據報有30個外交人員反對修例</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歐盟28國 + 美國 + 日本"},{"pid":"2b7299d2e5c1df5cf3cc95fa23e00fcea34b0d7e","tid":1178423,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"再嘈唔俾你地再係香港做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e0c9be2f642568ccf38998ade8318f9c414bc1","tid":1178423,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"777:關你撚事,唔回應個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}